fields.description:
In a repository (owned by a team account) source page, when you click the breadcrumb that links to a project, it gives a broken page.

!3011257082-repo_project_link.png|thumbnail!

h3. Expected Result
The project page should show

h3. Actual Result
The project page isn&#x27;t showing

h3. Workaround
For now, you can add open and close curly braces on the project URL to make it work.

{code}
#!python

https://bitbucket.org/account/user/{UUID_HERE}/projects/PROJECT
{code}

Or, change the UUID in the URL to the team account&#x27;s username.

{code}
#!python

https://bitbucket.org/account/user/USERNAME_HERE/projects/PROJECT
{code}
